*IPS display
*HDR
""AMD Freesync
*75Hz refresh rate and
*32"" screen size
Trusting LG and Amazon I ordered it on the day of launch only to be disappointed by the poor build quality(See images)
Uneven panel gaps
Unreasonably high screen(IPS) bleeding

One of the other reasons I opted for this monitor was the support of a feature called Dual Controller where one can control 2 machines with one set of keyboard and mouse basically magic! Sadly found out that a necessary part of using this feature called Picture by picture is not supported rendering the 'Dual controller' useless. Also dosent work with VPN connection which many of us need on work PCs"
