316,4 out of 5,"Sharp images, vivid colours, responsive monitor. It's a gorgeous IPS panel (anti-glare). This packages a premium experience for a not-so-premium price.

My qualms:

The monitor wobbles a bit when using the buttons, so be mindful of that.

There is a significant amount of IPS glow under low light conditions. If that bothers you, look for a non-IPS panel.

In general:

Ideal for desk usage. Stand won't swivel so usage is restricted to the horizontal mode. You get the standard port setup - 1 VGA, 1 HDMI. It'll get the job done for the average user. I believe it's an 8-bit, so professional photo editing is not the ideal use case.

Setup from the box is ridiculously easy. The quick setup manual's pretty helpful in case you get stuck."
