352,4.2 out of 5,"Well besides all the pros and cons, no one seems to tell u abt:
1. the 16 amp power cable which won't fit ur 6 amp normal socket. But don't worry u can use ur normal 6 amp power cable from ur older computer.
2. No display port cable or dp cable.
Without which u can't turn on freesync on or gsync adaptability on. U can't just buy any dp cable. Do some research before u buy. I am still looking for one.
3. Do check ur unit after receiving it. U can use "" eizo monitor test"". Google it. It comes with simple instruction.
4. 24.5 inch monitor compared to 32 inch TV is shown in picture.
5. Rest is gud so far. Total satisfaction is a subjective matter. So u can't just listen to someone's review. Do ur research first. Think critically and logically.
