1. Model Dell E2420HS Monitor, 24 inch
2. Sound, speaker -
- It has Inbuilt speaker, very good speaker
- It has additional extra speaker integration plug-able port for dell speakers
3. Ports
- 1 HDMI port - HDCP support is there with HDMI port
- 1 VGA
4. Design - Slim design, better quality, small side and top edges
5. Monitor configuration button is at front
6. Stand - Height adjustable stand (The one shown in amazon item picture is wrong) , it is sturdy
7. This model support ""Dell Display Manager"" software, which helps you to organize windows easily

Ideal for professional to work at home, photo,video editing

Very good monitor, with this price range with Speaker and slim one !!!"
