487,4.4 out of 5,"The Lenovo monitor is a good monitor with 75Hz refresh rate and QHD IPS Panel.
There are edge bleeds on the monitor, especially at the top, which is forgivable for an IPS panel.

What is even worse is that the seller Appario Retail sent me the monitor with defective pixels ""4 times"".
Normally Amazon allows only 1 replacement, so I had to return the order after finding that 2 times I had dead pixels in the monitor.

Then I proceeded with another order, hoping that this time situations would improve.
Unfortunately, the 3rd monitor (in the 2nd order) also had defective pixels, which made me upset and I chose a reeplacement.

Sadly, the 4th monitor sold by these fellows have 4 dead pixels in it. I would have to live with it now.

So guys, never ever purchase this monitor from Appario Retail Private Ltd.
Its quite shocking that a reputed seller sent defective items 4 times!"
