551,4.7 out of 5,"Ok, I was little skeptical about buying this monitor from Amazon as there were very limited reviews and the product was new but I believed in Samsung and ordered it. Boy this monitor is gorgeous.
Pros,
1) Punchy colors, good color accuracy, deep blacks (don't expect amoled level).
2) Three side bezel less design.
3) No dead pixels on the screen.
4) 75hz out of the box.
5) Made by Samsung that means no need to worry about servicing.
6) Supports vesa mount.
7) Comes with eye care feature (which is basically blue light cutter) out of the box.
Cons,
1) No builtin speakers and No audio jack for audio out.
2) Little too bright for my liking (I always keep the brightness below 25).

This monitor supports AMD freesync and refresh rates upto 75Hz, I don't have AMD GPU on my laptop to test freesync but surprisingly, I was able to set the refresh rate to 75Hz without Freesync (Please find the attached image). I was bit worried about dead pixels issue which is very common with most of the budget IPS panels but again I was pleasantly surprised to see no dead pixels on the screen (verified on Deadpixelbuddy)

Also I was able to authenticate the product and register it online with Samsung India to claim 36 months warranty. Happy with the seller for selling Samsung genuine products.

I couldn't test the gaming performance as I don't run games on my laptop, will try to update this review once I'm able to enjoy gaming session on this screen.

Peace.."
