622,3.8 out of 5,"Just got the monitor an hour back. The monitor itself is so light and thin, I thought it's just a cardboard and missed it in the first glance. Digged deep in the package to find my monitor!
But then I realized the one I thought as card board is the monitor. My god it is so light. Believe me, I am not exaggerating.
Once I unpacked the monitor in 2 minutes I was able to connect to the laptop and had my second monitor working.
The pixel quality is good and text is also sharp. Brightness is also well adequate if you are working indoors.
Color reproduction is also very good.
I was looking for Asus or Lenovo portable monitors since they are much cheaper than this monitor. However, those monitors work only with USB C ports. But this one can work with HDMI and USB both, that's the main advantage. My laptop anyway supports HMDI and it was a easy plug and play with out needing any additional hardware or driver.

One thing that the seller or even the Cloudwalker website doesn't mention is the contents of the package.
The package comes with
- Standard USB C,
- HDMI to HDMI mini
- USB 2.0 to USB C cable as weill

I am happy with my purchase. I can store my monitor and laptop safely in the wardrobe after my work everyday.
My desk looks clean after work.

The cover is sturdy and nice. Overall build quality is excellent. If you have money go for it."
