1. Best monitor within 6.5 k budget.
2. Its resolution need to be adjustd initially.
3. Adjust the resolution by playing 4k content from youtube also play the same content in your high end graphics based mobile parllaly so monitor color and brightness, contrast can be adjusted to achieve best result.
4. Fullhd movies played excellent with natural color.
5. Best part of this monitor is one can work more than 6 hours without eye strain. I tested 4 hours working continuously ,felt excellent.
6. No heat observed after 8 hours continually working .

