684,4.3 out of 5,"PROS:
- All required tools are provided
- Feels sturdy
- Somewhat ok instructional manual, though seller/company should upload some assembly video to youtube.

CONS:
-The product is extreemely diificult to assemble.
-To fit the screws in the groove it requires lot of effort.
-Does not feel like gas spring operated. I have used gas spring arms in my office earlier and they are very smooth in operating.
- However this one has arms which are extreemely tight and requires to use the alex screws to loosen and adjust.
-Even after assembling the arm, moving it requires lot of effort to move it around.

OVERALL - It is better to search for other products which cost a bit more but which are truely gas spring operated and have smooth mechanism. Do not believe on all the positive reviews. If you want your monitor to be stationary then definitely buy it otherwise if you require some sort of movement or tilting avoid this product."
