725,4.5 out of 5,"Actual dimensions:
L -44cm, W - 20cm, H - 5cm
Inner dimensions (if you want to put something underneath) -
H- 3.5cm, L - 36-40cm (angle)

Bought this specifically to keep my keyboard underneath, because of the false dimensions, it's too small to do so.
The product took waay too long to come, 10 days to be exact, 5 days past the expected delivery time.

Build quality - Average. There are visible holes through the wood, where the nails were hammered in. They didn't even try to make it look presentable, that's what you get when you spend only 999 I guess. Otherwise, it holds up. I'd be surprised if it didn't though, being so small.
I wouldn't bother using this as a monitor stand anyway, because it doesn't make much of a difference in height. Save up and buy a vesa mount monitor arm.

If you're planning on buying this, keep these things in mind."
