2. Love the ultra wide screen
3. Easy connectivity even with MacBook

Things I’m not happy about:
1. Very noticeable IPS flow, but we can’t really do anything about it. It happens with all IPS screens. Just wanted to mention that is a bit more noticeable when the screen completely goes black in movies or if you work on photo/video edits
2. While viewing from different angles, the colors are accurate, but the screen suffers a lot of glare and the IPS glow is even more noticeable then

There you go I have mentioned what I feel about this.

But I’m keeping this unit, cause IPS glow is just unavoidable. Hoping the monitor will perform great.

Video editing will be kickass ok this thing!!!"
