879,4.3 out of 5,"The 27 inch monitor by Samsung is a great buy especially for work. It has an inbuilt eye saver mode which enables a blue light filter. The contrast ratio is good and picture quality is great. It's very bright when at full brightness so don't work in the dark with this at full throttle.

4 stars because they could have provided a HDMI cable instead of a VGA and also the port could have been vertical instead of horizontal connection which hinders placing close to the wall"
