1003,4.4 out of 5,"Dear All,

I received the monitor as agreed in 2 days.
I was using laptop earlier and due considering WFH - I purchased this monitor for office work.
As far as office work use - I am fully satisfied. Those who are WFH and using laptop screen, guys, Please switch to monitor like this considering eye care.
I am not gaming fan so can not comment on same. The youTube quality was okay to good.

Why did purchased this product:
1. Budget: I do not wanted to go beyond 9000 Rs.
2. Size: I dont want to have more than 22 inch size. Can our eyes catch more than that?
3. Technical: I wanted IPS panel (for sure) - 100% Recommended
4. Ports: One HDMI was sufficient for my laptop ( 1 VGA is bonus)
5. Country of Origin of this product is India ( Yes, Of course my preference)

Cons:
No USB port ( Why do we need?)
No speakers ( Why did WFH need it?) Laptop has speakers!"
