1030,5 out of 5,"1. Packaging was nice, though bit damaged from top right corner in 1000 km long journey from Maharashtra to Delhi, but thanks to Internal Thick Thermocol for saving the Product.
2. Product is Superb, Big enough to split screen and do multi-tasking simultaneously
3. Comes with 5 Preset viewing mode such as Standard, Internet, Games, Easy Read, and LowBlue mode, which can further be customized.
4. Comes with different refresh rate, 50Hz is good for normal Reading, regular surfing, coding, programming whereas High Refresh rate of 75Hz is available for detailed work like Graphics Designing.
5. Flexible stand to adjust viewing angle, which is little bit tight initially but works fine later.
6. Do not forget to bring down Sharpness, Brightness and Contrast Rate manually on monitor If you want to safeguard your eye and want to use this for longer period of time.
7. Do Register product on Philips website, and don't forget to install respective drivers from their site."
