1034,4.4 out of 5,"I bought it for 8200.
Pros:
1) 2019 Model
2) Anti-glare
3)Low-blue light feature
4)Good resolution for a 21.5""(if you know what I mean)
Cons:
1) Not stylish unlike the 22es.
2) Not wall-mountable.
