UPDATE 0:
The screen dims and brightens for a fraction of a second every now and then.
UPDATE 1:
Just got the replacement today.
Even this has the same problem.
It looks like it's an inherent problem in this model.
I'm guessing the condition might worsen with time.
Reply if you notice it too.
UPDATE 2:
The flicker is actually a thing in this model. If you are someone like me who gets annoyed with the flickering then you should buy a monitor with flicker-free technology.
I returned this product for BenQ 24"" which comes with flicker-free technology."
